    <h1>Erectile dysfunction is common &#8212; and it&#8217;s treatable</h1>
    <p>It affects men of every age, and it&#8217;s rarely talked about. Here&#8217;s what tends to cause it, and how a short, confidential conversation with a doctor can help.</p>
